%N A015208 Inverse of 1199th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015208 Periodic with period length 1199. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015208 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015208/b015208.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015208 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1199.
